s/563587168","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546253999,"updated_time":1546253999,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e有我当年的风范。（建议你发布前再检查检查）\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560454605,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"753d8d93574591c259941bfe7a0daa8b","url_token":"jiang-huai-82","name":"予淮","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9d4a4cbaa62039c91a571c10376d6073_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9d4a4cbaa62039c91a571c10376d6073_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/753d8d93574591c259941bfe7a0daa8b","user_type":"people","headline":"愿凭清风，愿以盛放。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560454605","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545839027,"updated_time":1545839117,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e无论如何 结果无论对错 都很厉害了吧\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e至少比一些只知道冷嘲热讽的人不知道强了多少倍 这个问题下有温情 更多是看热闹的冷漠吧 事不关己 就可以随便践踏别人的自尊了吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个高中生 只知道初等数论 却敢去尝试这么难的数学猜想 这不是我们所提倡的事情吗 一个社会 如果没有这样的人涌现 反而有一堆人在一旁拼了命地把人从探索的路上拉回去 不是件特别可悲的事情吗\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我不是说他一定对 我数学不好 对数学好的人我一直抱着敬佩又仰慕的态度 我也不赞成这个问题的问法 真的证明出来 清北留不住你 但是下面一堆人的否定和嘲讽真的特别让人寒心  难道一个高中生的梦想就要受到这类无情的抨击 各类数学大神可以来帮忙纠正 但是怎么也轮不到对数论一窍不通 就等着数学大神证明正误后扑上来嘲笑的人批判\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e希望每个闪闪发光的梦想都能得到尊重\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主加油❤\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以上。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560673220,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c17a2fa8908b8dfc9b80fc3170d4d13e","url_token":"zhi-hao-yu","name":"支浩宇","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c17a2fa8908b8dfc9b80fc3170d4d13e","user_type":"people","headline":"广州天河工作","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560673220","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545878467,"updated_time":1545878467,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不能，参见日本数学家望月新一，此人2012年8月宣称证明了ABC猜想，到现在六年过去了，数学界没有几个人能看懂他的证明，也无法确认他的证明是否正确。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于一个高中生来说，假定你的证明是正确的，且能在6年时间内被数学界承认 — 这六年时间足够你读另一所大学读到大四了，更何况6年的时间还不一定足够。历史上很多科学发现是在发现者去世后才得到承认的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以，有好好的正常高考上大学的路你不走，非要傻走一条不知道要等多少年才通的路？ 如果真的这么傻，那就算你上100个北大也只是高分低能的废物。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562190921,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d32e0bfa2f18e8e2ee4eb11dfc73a17b","url_token":"xcgdgp","name":"xcgdgp","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d32e0bfa2f18e8e2ee4eb11dfc73a17b","user_type":"people","headline":"会计 审计 证券","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562190921","thumbnail