a342a6f293b9df82954ed552b4b976","user_type":"people","headline":"IT工程师，公众号：林伟彦笔记","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561054864","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545911829,"updated_time":1545911829,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e得多看不起哥德巴赫猜想啊。真解决了，数学功底得到什么程度啊。都能写进教科书啦。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说句不客气的。世界顶尖学校求着你去。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560654452,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"9b1f8c2f96cb9b239a1fb6a523694692","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560654452","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545877158,"updated_time":1545877158,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e费马大定理 已经被证明了。提问者可以参考一下证明过程以及证明者的资历。如果谁（不管你是高中生还是初中生）能证明哥德巴赫猜想，那数学方面的造诣肯定不比其低，别说保送清华北大了，直接去其数学系任教时没问题的。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":564032044,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5ad770c840e1fd05a9f379633967ef57","url_token":"time-runner","name":"runner time","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/41fa7bd1118585e01de0d629d2ea40ce_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/41fa7bd1118585e01de0d629d2ea40ce_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5ad770c840e1fd05a9f379633967ef57","user_type":"people","headline":"人与人的人生是不同的。故事的小屌丝，从出生那年就是屌丝。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564032044","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546323035,"updated_time":1546323937,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e能证明哥德巴赫猜想还需要保送清华北大？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我特么也是醉了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e全世界所有人都会把你当成数学大师，光奖金加起来好像就几百万美元，再送你各种名誉教授头衔，终身衣食无忧。国家把你当大熊猫供着，到哪都是享受国家特殊待遇和补贴。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你告诉我这种人的追求只是全世界前100名都排不到的清华北大？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这种中国式特色思维也是没谁了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你丫高兴，直接去清北数学系当教授算了，当学生多浪费资源啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e任何证明出来的人，不敢说比欧拉强，但至少智商比欧拉高。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e欧拉是谁？历史前五的数学家，上帝级别的人物。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你先把拉格朗日比下去再说，人家19岁就当大学教授了，是欧拉的指定接班人。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562174699,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ac220a531e2b0dd3b8ad826bff3faa81","url_token":"yi-mei-ku-bi-de-gao-zhong-sheng","name":"一枚苦逼的高中生","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ac220a531e2b0dd3b8ad826bff3faa81","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562174699","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"cre